on PointPositive aPoint
  [  0] getparam 0 .............................. <aPoint>
  [  2] pushint8 1 .............................. <1>
  [  4] getparam 0 .............................. <aPoint>
  [  6] pushint8 1 .............................. <1>
  [  8] pusharglist 2 ........................... <aPoint, 1>
  [ 10] objcall 18 .............................. <aPoint[1]>
  [ 12] pusharglist 1 ........................... <aPoint[1]>
  [ 14] extcall 329 ............................. <VarPositive(aPoint[1])>
  [ 17] pusharglistnoret 3 ...................... <aPoint, 1, VarPositive(aPoint[1])>
  [ 19] objcall 81 .............................. aPoint[1] = VarPositive(aPoint[1])
  [ 21] getparam 0 .............................. <aPoint>
  [ 23] pushint8 2 .............................. <2>
  [ 25] getparam 0 .............................. <aPoint>
  [ 27] pushint8 2 .............................. <2>
  [ 29] pusharglist 2 ........................... <aPoint, 2>
  [ 31] objcall 18 .............................. <aPoint[2]>
  [ 33] pusharglist 1 ........................... <aPoint[2]>
